dc_title_s: Parcels Fond du Lac County, WI 2013
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Parcels_2013.gdb.[The Parcels layer depicts tax parcels within Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin. It has a variety of sources such as deed descriptions, subdivision plats, and certified survey maps. The County Land Information Department maintains these files.The data is current through December 31, 2013. For City of Fond du Lac parcels, contact: City of Fond du Lac GIS/Maps Dept]
